title: Grateful Dead Live at The Omni on 1994-04-01
description:
Set 1

Picasso Moon-> Deal, Wang Dang Doodle, Dire Wolf, Black Throated Wind*, Bird Song

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Box Of Rain, Estimated Prophet-> He's Gone-> That Would Be Something-> Drums-> Space-> The Other One-> Wharf Rat-> Turn On Your Love Light, E: Brokedown Palace

* Weir on acoustic

reviews.review_text: - Quite hot work, for almost any year, but especially for this year. The thing is, there were both very good and very horrible shows this year: the 2 Seattle shows were the worst and best shows I'd ever seen, right in a pair. The Black-Throated here is hotly jammy at the end. Nice Lovelight. Jerry sounds introspective but on his game.
